references: Related: CF 204100, CF 204220, CF 204233. Amending: Ord 45382
summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 6, Block 2, Wilcox Addition; unplatted portion of the northeast quarter of the northeast quarter of the southwest quarter of Section 27-24-4; and Lots 5, 6 and 7, Block 56, West Seattle Land and Improvement Company's 2nd Plat; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-251 and 17-198, respectively.
